text: Homelix cruciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1937, originally misspelled as "Homelix cruciatus". It is known from Uganda.BioLib.cz - Homelix cruciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1937
